{
  "message": "test(conformance): add polynomial adversarial cases (+12)\n\nPolynomial adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- poly_empty_coefficients: zero polynomial handling\n- poly_single_coefficient: constant polynomial\n- poly_eval_at_zero: x=0 evaluation\n- poly_with_nan_coefficient: NaN propagation\n- poly_eval_at_inf: infinity evaluation\n- polyadd_empty_plus_nonempty: empty + non-empty\n- polymul_by_zero_poly: multiplication by zero polynomial\n- polyroots_constant: roots of constant (no roots)\n- polyroots_linear: single root case\n- polyder_constant: derivative of constant\n- polyint_with_constant: integration constant handling\n- polyfit_perfect_line: exact fit case\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
